No. 8,

Orig.

Arizona v. California et al. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 440 U. S. 942.]

Memorandum and Report of the Special Master on preliminary issues received and ordered filed. Motion of Arizona et al. for leave to file exceptions to the Memorandum and Report of the Special Master denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of these matters.
